# Per-agent local history (~/.claude/history.jsonl, plans/) is high-churn and
# does not delta-compress well. Backed up via per-agent orphan branches:
#   agent-history-<host>-<agent-id>
# See scripts/hooks/snapshot-local-orphan.sh and AGENTS.md §12.
agents/*/*/local/
